      <xref linkend="gtk-doc"/>,
      <xref linkend="qt4"/>,
      <xref linkend="valgrind"/>,
      <xref linkend="wpa_supplicant"/> (built with D-Bus support),
      <ulink url="http://libteam.org/">libteam</ulink>, and
      <ulink url="http://www.freedesktop.org/software/ModemManager/">
      ModemManager</ulink>,
    </para>

